Text: You're a god. It's torrents like this that make me glad to be a filthy, theiving brigand. Someone out of generosity uploading a beloved semi-obscure film for others to discover. In spite of the fact that I live in the ass end of nowhere with a terrible connection, I'm going to continue seeding for a long time.
This is why I joined. So I could finally appreciate these classic films.

Jesus, yes. Thank you so much

I'm glad someone remembers to put this stuff up!
